{"tid":1488890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家以後唔好再用「割席」一詞，改用「錫春袋」。","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T18:50:22.000Z","uid":4396,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eb85b5460c94ca6fce448f17d8e1f2b69eeb69f3","tid":1488890,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"我知今日有班巴打精蟲上腦令部分巴打絲打唔高興，但人非聖賢，請大家唔好輕易就講「割席」。就好似拍拖咁，下下鬧交都講分手的話，真係會好傷心同心淡。唔通你會因爲某些巴打的行為而支持送中咩。<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家以後如果對手足有咩不滿就大大聲講「再犯同樣的錯誤就錫你春袋呀喇！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信佢地已經知錯。請大家依一分鐘起忘記隻老母狗，一起宣傳接下來的行動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n堅持到底！勿忘諸位烈士寄望！"},{"pid":"a462879ce366b8e328b8e356bd55fcf1b6934f3d","tid":1488890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"唔推你會唔會錫我袋袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33da1fd39df4eb1a92a16553d30ecb1c5c6a7788","tid":1488890,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a462879ce366b8e328b8e356bd55fcf1b6934f3d","tid":1488890,"uid":69864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"唔推你會唔會錫我袋袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a94e9b2c1ccd893c5f5ef8d22840bf04661a25","tid":1488890,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmZOxCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2